data.title: Kiko Navarro & DJ Fudge feat. Kaleta
data.meta_description:
Douwe by Kiko Navarro & DJ Fudge feat. Kaleta, released 05 May 2023

1. Douwe (Original Mix)
2. Douwe (Original Mix Edit)
3. Douwe (Dub Mix)
4. Douwe (Instrumental Mix)

Something really special next on FOLIAGE as we welcome the incredible hybrid sounds of KIKO NAVARRO & DJ FUDGE feat. KALETA and the single DOUWE.

Originally from France and now based in Spain DJ FUDGE is truly one of the most versatile and prolific house music producers of his generation.

KIKO NAVARRO has carved out an enviable reputation across the globe for his distinctive and highly personal brand of House music. Born on Mallorca, KIKO NAVARROâ€™s voyage of sonic discovery has been going strong for almost three decades now.

Guitarist KALETA (real name, LEON LIGAN-MAJEK) hails from Porto Novo in the Republic of Benin, but lived all his adolescent life in Lagos, Nigeria. KALETA has played, toured and recorded with FELA KUTI, KING SUNNY ADE, LAURYN HILL and MAJEK FASHEK to mention but a few. KALETA is currently the frontman of New York based Afro-Funk group SUPER YAMBA BAND as well as AKOYA AFROBEAT ENSEMBLE and his own band KALETA & ZOZO AFROBEAT.
